The way I created the game and implemented the instructions from the pdf is laid out below:

,:	item pickup command. Picks up first item on stack if their is a

w:	wears an item and is accessible only in players inventory
t:	takes off an item equipped and stores it in inventory if there is room otherwise it is dropped, accessible only from players equipment
d:	drop an item and is accessible in inventory or equipment
x:	expunge an item and is accessible while handling ordinary input(not in inventory or equipment)
i: 	list PC inventory and accessible while handling ordinary input
e:	list PC equipment and accessible while handling ordinary input
I:	Inspects an item while in player inventory
L:	Looks at a monster, accessible while handling ordinary input
